How to Run
1. Make the script executable
```bash
chmod +x hardware/hdl/sim/run_sim.sh
```

2. Run simulators
```bash
# Run default testbench
./run_sim.sh

# Run specific testbench in GUI mode
./run_sim.sh -t tb_lif_neuron -g

# Clean and run with waveforms
./run_sim.sh -c -w

# Run with coverage
./run_sim.sh -t tb_top -cov
```
